## Priority Definitions

| Priority | Meaning | Implementation Timeline |
|---|---|---|
| P0 | Critical for business decisions. Implement before launch. | Day 1 |
| P1 | Important for optimization. Implement within first sprint. | Week 1-2 |
| P2 | Nice to have for deeper analysis. Implement when capacity allows. | Month 1 |
| P3 | Low priority. Implement only if specifically needed. | Backlog |
